{"title":"为海南岛歌唱","authors":["袁水拍"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":4,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"为海南岛歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁水拍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海岛阵地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧澄澄大海左右绕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌油油岩下隐大炮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红胖胖战士正年少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山东口音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有说又有笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山坡下把兵练，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"食堂里办学校，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把家乡的鸡冠花种遍交通壕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为祖国平安，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军安家在南海岛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钱铃双刀舞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一人打钱铃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一人舞白刃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铃棒护腰身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双刀驰流星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀劈左，头避右，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀刺右，身如钩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀如雨点眼如电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身随刀光左右闪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年黎族为自卫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从小练武习攻守。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奇妙啊，是力的舞蹈！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚健啊，是美的战斗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海南万宝岛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海南岛，风光好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四季花开春不老，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椰林摇曳红砂路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云青山五指高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水陆金银库，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山藏珍宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不愁耕地缺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但嫌人手少。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大革命后根据地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗高举没有倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海螺吹出胜利曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"琼歌再唱公社好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不分汉黎苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结坚又牢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着党的总路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设海南万宝岛！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}